INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------

----

To install, do:

./configure
make
make install

----

To install to a custom directory, do:

./configure --prefix=<custom_dir>
make
make install

----

To uninstall, do:

make uninstall

----

For a clean re-installation, do:

make distclean
./configure
make
make install

----

NOTES: * The RCS software is required; you'll get errors if it is missing.
       * If RCS is installed to a non-standard locaton, modify rvi.cc.
	   * Restricted vi is also known as rvi, adjust PATH or aliases as needed.

----
